<lb n="0489c05" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1323</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0489c06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0489007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，（佛說）＋除【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0489007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】＊，佛說除【明】【甲】＊，【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><app n="0489007"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">佛說除</rdg></app><note n="0489007" type="rest" place="foot">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>一切疾病陀羅尼<note n="0489008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（圓仁請來）細註【甲】</note><note n="0489008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經(圓仁請來)【甲】</note><app n="0489008"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經<note place="inline">圓仁請來</note></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0489c07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0489c08" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0489009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【宋】【元】【甲】，（（唐三藏沙門大廣智））八字【明】</note><note n="0489009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…門）四十一字【大】，大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智【宋】【元】【甲】，唐三藏沙門大廣智【明】</note><app cb:word-count="41" n="0489009"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0489c09" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0489c10" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0489c11" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0489c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0489c1201">如是我聞。一<note n="0489010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">時＝切【明】</note><note n="0489010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，切【明】</note><app n="0489010"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>薄伽梵。住室羅<note n="0489011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">伐＝筏【三】【甲】</note><note n="0489011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伐【大】，筏【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489011"><lem wit="【大】">伐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">筏</rdg></app>城逝多
<lb n="0489c13" ed="T"/>林給孤長者園。與大苾芻眾千二百五十人
<lb n="0489c14" ed="T"/>俱。<note n="0489012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眾多諸大＝及眾大多【三】，及眾多大【甲】</note><note n="0489012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾多諸大【大】，及眾大多【宋】【元】【明】，及眾多大【甲】</note><app n="0489012"><lem wit="【大】">眾多諸大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">及眾大多</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">及眾多大</rdg></app>菩薩摩訶薩。爾時世尊告阿難
<lb n="0489c15" ed="T"/>陀言。阿難陀有陀羅尼。能除世間一切疾病。
<lb n="0489c16" ed="T"/>汝當受持讀誦通利如理作意。即說密言曰。</p>
<lb n="0489c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0489c1701" cb:type="dharani">怛儞也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">一</note>尾摩黎尾摩黎<note place="inline">二</note>嚩曩俱枳黎
<lb n="0489c18" ed="T"/><note place="inline">三</note>室唎<note place="inline">二合</note>末底<note place="inline">丁以<note n="0489013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】【甲】</note><note n="0489013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反【大】，切【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489013"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">切</rdg></app>四</note>軍拏黎<note place="inline">五</note>嫩奴鼻<note place="inline">六</note>印
<lb n="0489c19" ed="T"/>捺囉<note place="inline">二合</note>儗𩕳<note place="inline">二合七</note>母隷娑嚩<note place="inline">二<note n="0489014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0489014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489014"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">合引</rdg></app></note><note n="0489015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引八）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0489015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶(引八)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489015"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">訶<note place="inline">引八</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0489c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0489c2001">佛告阿難陀。此陀羅尼若誦持者。宿食不消
<lb n="0489c21" ed="T"/><note n="0489016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">癨＝霍【三】【甲】</note><note n="0489016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癨【大】，霍【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489016"><lem wit="【大】">癨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">霍</rdg></app>亂風黃痰癊。患痔<note n="0489017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瘻淋＝瘺淋瀝【宋】【明】【甲】，痛淋瀝【元】</note><note n="0489017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瘻淋【大】，瘺淋瀝【宋】【明】【甲】，痛淋瀝【元】</note><app n="0489017"><lem wit="【大】">瘻淋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">瘺淋瀝</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">痛淋瀝</rdg></app>上氣。嗽<note n="0489018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虐＝瘧【宋】【甲】</note><note n="0489018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虐【大】，瘧【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0489018"><lem wit="【大】">虐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】">瘧</rdg></app>寒熱
<lb n="0489c22" ed="T"/>頭痛<note n="0489019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">半＝背【三】【甲】</note><note n="0489019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">半【大】，背【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0489019"><lem wit="【大】">半</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">背</rdg></app>痛。著鬼魅者悉得除差。我以佛眼觀
<lb n="0489c23" ed="T"/>見彼人。諸天魔梵沙門婆羅門能作障難。除
<lb n="0489c24" ed="T"/>非決定業報盡者。餘無能違越作其障難。如
<lb n="0489c25" ed="T"/>來應供正遍知說。一切有情中如來為尊勝。
<lb n="0489c26" ed="T"/>一切法中離欲法<note n="0489020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（為）ィ＋尊【甲】</note><note n="0489020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊【大】，為尊【校異-甲】</note><app n="0489020"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">為尊</rdg></app>。一切眾中僧伽為尊。以
<lb n="0489c27" ed="T"/>此誠實言願我及一切有情。食飲喫啖入腹
<lb n="0489c28" ed="T"/>消化得正安樂。娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note n="0489021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【三】</note><note n="0489021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0489021"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0489c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0489c2901">爾時世尊說是經已。諸苾芻僧并諸菩薩摩
<pb n="0490a" xml:id="T21.1323.0490a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0490a01" ed="T"/>訶薩。一切大眾天龍八部。受持佛語歡喜奉
<lb n="0490a02" ed="T"/>行。</p>
<lb n="0490a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><app type="star" corresp="#0489007"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">佛說除</rdg></app>一切疾病陀羅尼<note n="0490001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧云貞享元甲子年九月二十一夕挍之點之是為明日指授諸徒也淨嚴四十六載，元祿十六年三月十八日以淨嚴和上之本再挍了尊教</note>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>